OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,F"I apologise to our passengers for the
OL,8,Finconvenience they suffered. We've
OL,9,Ftaken corrective measures and added
OL,10,Fadditional aircraft capacity in terms
OL,11,Fof our fleet and we're ready to start
OL,12,Fthe summer season."
OL,14,FMr Bezuidenhout also commented on the
OL,15,Frecent news that and replacing it by
OL,16,Fleasing two smaller planes instead.
