OL,3,CAurigny boss apologises for
OL,4,C'inconvenience' caused by flight
OL,5,Cdisruption
OL,7,FHe explained: "In reality, a jet
OL,8,Foperation is not suitable for such a
OL,9,Fshort sector, the 36-minute flight to
OL,10,FGatwick. It is too short and damages
OL,11,Fthe aircraft and impacts its
OL,12,Freliability."
OL,14,FHe went on to add that having the jet
OL,15,Fas part of their fleet is not "cost
OL,16,Feffective" as it is almost 10-years-
OL,17,Fold and has an expensive service due
OL,18,Fsoon.
