OL,7,FThe aircraft will stop scheduled
OL,8,Fflights at the end of April but stay
OL,9,Fas a back up until the end of May.
OL,11,FMr Bezuidenhout also confirmed that
OL,12,Fdemand around the Easter bank holidays
OL,13,Fhad been "quite robust" with around 5%
OL,14,Fmore passengers booked on services
OL,15,Fcompared to last year.
